OL,4,G0600FThe Best of the 70s
OL,5,     GA look back at the wide variety
OL,6,     Gof sports covered by ITV during
OL,7,     Gthe 1970s - from horse racing to
OL,8,     Gtable football and Formula One to
OL,9,     Gdarts - that includes many
OL,10,     Gmemorable moments.
OL,11,G0620FThe Big Match Revisited
OL,12,     GBrian Moore presents a special FA
OL,13,     GCup Fourth Round edition from
OL,14,     GJanuary 1978 as West Ham United
OL,15,     Gface QPR, Bristol Rovers
OL,16,     Gchallenge Southampton, and
OL,17,     GMiddlesbrough take on Everton.
